==Filmography==
===As actor=== {{multiple image <!-- Essential parameters --> | align = right | direction = vertical | width = 180 <!-- Image 1 --> | image1 = Biograph poster2.jpg | alt1 = | caption1 = Poster for ''[[Three Friends (film)|Three Friends]]'', 1913 <!-- Image 2 --> | image2 = The Wanderer - D.W. Griffiths - 1913, Biograph - EYE FLM73625 - OB 685547.webm | alt2 = | caption2 = ''[[The Wanderer (1913 film)|The Wanderer]]'', 1913 <!-- Image 3 --> | image3 =The Quitter.jpg | alt3 = | caption3 = Ad for ''[[The Quitter]]'', 1916 <!-- Image 4 --> | image4 = Dorian's Divorce.jpg | alt4 = | caption4 = Ad for ''[[Dorian's Divorce]]'', 1916 <!-- Image 5 --> | image5 = The Millionaire's Double.jpg | alt5 = | caption5 = Ad for ''[[The Millionaire's Double]]'', 1917 <!-- Image 6 --> | image6 = Lionel Barrymore The Copperhead Motion Picture Classic 1920.png | alt6 = | caption6 = Barrymore in ''[[The Copperhead]]'', 1920 <!-- Image 7 --> | image7 = The Devil's Garden (1920) ad.jpg | alt7 = | caption7 = Lantern slide for ''[[The Devil's Garden]]'', 1920; Barrymore—on the right—appeared with his wife, [[Doris Rankin]], who sits on the left. <!-- Image 8 --> | image8 = The Face in the Fog (1922) 2.jpg | alt8 = | caption8 = Barrymore and [[Seena Owen]] in ''[[The Face in the Fog]]'', 1922 <!-- Image 9 --> | image9 = Ah, Wilderness! (1935) trailer 1.jpg | alt9 = | caption9 = Barrymore in ''[[Ah, Wilderness! (film)|Ah, Wilderness!]]'', 1935 <!-- Image 10 --> | image10 = Lionel Barrymore in David Copperfield trailer 2.jpg | alt10 = | caption10 = Barrymore in a trailer for ''[[David Copperfield (1935 film)|David Copperfield]]'', 1935 <!-- Image 11 --> | image11 = Lionelcamille.jpg | alt11 = | caption11 = Barrymore in ''[[Camille (1936 film)|Camille]]'', 1936 }} {{multiple image <!-- Essential parameters --> | align = right | direction = vertical | width = 180 <!-- Image 1 --> | image1 = A Family Affair 1937.JPG | alt1 = | caption1 = Poster for ''[[A Family Affair (1937 film)|A Family Affair]]'