ous Hussy]]''}} | {{sort|1936.4|1936}} | {{sort|Jackson|[[Andrew Jackson]]}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Gorgeous Hussy" /> |- ! scope="row" | ''[[Camille (1936 film)|Camille]]'' | {{sort|1936.5|1936}} | {{sort|Duval|Monsieur Duval}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Camille" /> |- ! scope="row" | {{sort|Family Affair|''[[A Family Affair (1937 film)|A Family Affair]]''}} | {{sort|1937.1|1937}} | {{sort|Hardy|Judge James K. Hardy}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Family Affair" /> |- ! scope="row" | ''[[Captains Courageous (1937 film)|Captains Courageous]]'' | {{sort|1937.2|1937}} | {{sort|Troop|Capt. Disko Troop}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Captains Courageous" /> |- ! scope="row" | ''[[Saratoga (film)|Saratoga]]'' | {{sort|1937.3|1937}} | {{sort|Clayton|Grandpa Clayton}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Saratoga" /> |- ! scope="row" | ''[[Navy Blue and Gold (film)|Navy Blue and Gold]]'' | {{sort|1937.4|1937}} | {{sort|Dawes|Captain "Skinny" Dawes}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Navy Blue and Gold" /> |- ! scope="row" | {{sort|Yank at Oxford|''[[A Yank at Oxford]]''}} | {{sort|1938.1|1938}} | {{sort|Sheridan|Dan Sheridan}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Yank at Oxford" /> |- ! scope="row" | ''[[Test Pilot (film)|Test Pilot]]'' | {{sort|1938.2|1938}} | {{sort|Drake|Howard B. Drake}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Test Pilot" /> |- ! scope="row" | ''[[You Can't Take It with You (film)|You Can't Take It with You]]'' | {{sort|1938.3|1938}} | {{sort|Vanderhof|Martin Vanderhof}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Can't Take It" /> |- ! scope="row" | ''[[Young Dr. Kildare]]'' | {{sort|1938.4|1938}} | {{sort|Gillespie|Dr. Leonard Gillespie}} | | style="text-align: center;" | <ref name="AFI: Young Kildare" /> |- ! scope="row" | ''[[Let Freedom Ring (1939 film)|Let Freedom Ring]]'' | {{sort|1939.1|1939}} | {{s